snippet.title: Major Amber Heard Update You Need To Know Now
snippet.description:
Major Amber Heard Update You Need To Know Now
Subscribe To InformOverload: http://bit.ly/2xB5CqA
Recent Uploads: https://bit.ly/2V7kA4s

If you’ve been following along with the Amber Heard and Johnny Depp case, then you likely know that Johnny lost his libel case against the publication The Sun, who referred to him as a Wife Beater. Following the ruling, which Depp and his legal team have made very clear they will appeal, while also continuing to claim his innocence, led to Depp being asked to resign from the film Fantastic Beasts. Now as of this recording, Amber is still on board to reprise her role as Mera in Aquaman 2, but we have some major updates you need to know.
